| 2 | No security headers (Helmet) | A05 – Misconfiguration | 🔴 Critical |
| 3 | Unauthenticated PII exposure | A01 – Broken Access Control | 🔴 Critical |
| 4 | No CORS policy | A05 – Misconfiguration | 🟠 Medium |
| 5 | No error handler / stack trace leak | A04 – Insecure Design | 🟠 Medium |
| 6 | Binds to all interfaces | A05 – Misconfiguration | 🟠 Medium |
| 7 | Hardcoded configuration | A05 – Misconfiguration | 🟠 Medium |
| 8 | No request logging | A09 – Logging Failures | 🟡 Low |
| 9 | Server fingerprinting | A05 – Misconfiguration | 🟡 Low |
| 10 | No proxy trust config | A05 – Misconfiguration | 🟡 Low |

